  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为唱片销售系统建一个ER图。核心是销售记录，每次销售要关联到具体的唱片，还要记录客户信息和购买数量。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ventas",
        "Discos",
        "numeroFactura",
        "nombreCliente",
        "cantidad"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Ventas作为销售主表。那客户信息您只打算存姓名吗？要不要把nombreCliente和apellidoCliente分开字段？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ventas",
        "nombreCliente",
        "apellidoCliente"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，分开存。另外Ventas里用disco作为外键关联到唱片表，一个销售记录对应一张唱片，但一张唱片可以被多次销售。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ventas",
        "disco",
        "Discos"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Ventas和Discos的关系我记为一对多，Ventas这边是可选的，Discos那边是必须的。现在来看Discos表还需要哪些属性？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ventas",
        "Discos",
        "tiene"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Discos要有codigo做主键，nombre是唱片名称，precio是价格。还需要关联到三个维度表：Generos音乐类型、Interprete演唱者、Sello唱片公司。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Discos",
        "codigo",
        "nombre",
        "precio",
        "Generos",
        "Interprete",
        "Sello"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这三个关联都是必须的，对吧？一张唱片必须有类型、演唱者和所属公司。那关系我都做成多对一，Discos这边可选还是必须？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Discos",
        "Generos",
        "Interprete",
        "Sello"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "都是必须的，每张唱片都要完整归属。对了，Generos除了nombre还要有个descripcion字段来描述风格特点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Generos",
        "nombre",
        "descripcion"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。Interprete表我放了nombre、apellido和fechaNacimiento，Sello表有email和domicilio，您看可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Interprete",
        "nombre",
        "apellido",
